{
  "stem": "12674.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately the way the world was made and everything, we didn't have anything-- I had made a tape, but that was the summer before he died.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have [INAUDIBLE] and a few Austrian folk songs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was still far better than any other amateur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- the soaring, fabulous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was so clear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was nine years old, I could tell when tenor was singing like he had dumplings in his throat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, there's an expression when somebody sings like that in German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I could tell because I was used to this clear singing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had a very beautiful voice too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I was about 10 years old, the teacher called my father to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she wanted to know if he was going to have the voice developed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, no, she wants to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She wants to be a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She wants to cut people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She wants to be a surgeon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she said, it is a gift that very few people had, that she we should do something about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Unfortunately, there was never any choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Two years later the world came apart at the seams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was sitting in back of a truck in the snow and singing on top of my lungs and the voice went.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But when I got married I still could reach a high C without any effort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But, of course, I never learned how to sing and breathe or anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have wanted to study medicine since I've been four years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had an old lady friend who owned the chickens-- my mother used to buy chicken stand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made friends with the old lady.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
